{"tid":2462450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【一票難求】MIRROR五月演唱會門票火速售罄　考慮加場兼推新歌滿足粉絲","createTime":"2021-03-26T04:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T04:38:46.000Z","uid":350584,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b62372af090400b1f04271d1b52d8d5a71b5c2ec","tid":2462450,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"超人氣組合MIRROR日前宣布將於5月6至8日舉行一連三場的《MIRROR&ldquo;ONE &amp; ALL&rdquo;LIVE 2021》，門票今日早上10時公開發售，因MIRROR粉絲太湧躍，一度令售票網站癱瘓，門票在半日內已全部售罄，大批粉絲因買不到票而失望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW2ggRKhLkxacbZxtuEg2V2LiKh88aLz5HU6v587JLs7k?filename=Q8KbEdq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8KbEdq.jpg&h=e26f1134&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed8a73fc3ca6b1e3a3b036d80ffcebe6005cb046","tid":2462450,"uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"由ViuTV大型選秀節目《全民造星》中出道的男子組合MIRROR於2018年底成軍出道，成員包括姜濤、楊樂文（Lokman）、陳卓賢（Ian）、江𤒹生（Anson Kong）、王智德（Alton）、盧瀚霆（Anson Lo）、呂爵安（Edan）、陳瑞輝（Frankie）、柳應廷（Jer）、李駿傑（Jeremy）、邱士縉（Stanley）和邱傲然（Tiger），人氣一直高企。<br />\n<br />\n在成軍兩周年，MIRROR早前宣布將在5月在九展舉行演唱會，暫定3場。<br />\n<br />\n門票今日早上10時公開發售，不少fans已全力撲飛。開賣後售票網站一度顯示系統長期繁忙，限定套裝在一小時內已經售罄，其後所有門票亦告沽清。"},{"pid":"74d7ffb9cb5d0e8e7940699ee3aa764132fd002c","tid":2462450,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfUsAPVC2e6GqctWNQ33xaYGB8KnukuXYGY7JXbwnGD4o?filename=E3mmg0G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3mmg0G.jpg&h=39f80e53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f9e7d17bfde24412ac83f763deec74cab8b825e","tid":2462450,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:13:42.000Z","msg":"今日除是演唱會開賣日，同日亦是MIRROR推出2021年第一首派台歌《WARRIOR》，官方宣傳照以12位成員穿上黑色西裝擺出型爆甫士，相信買不到飛的歌迷可暫時止渴。"},{"pid":"1e2fd32249d54427f7fd8a152f7644209767f86f","tid":2462450,"uid":34773,"like":1,"dislike":10,